hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 光致电离速率  
   $$\Gamma_{3c}
     =\int_{I_3}^\infty\sigma_3(E)\,c\,n_\gamma(E)\,dE
     =c\,\frac{8\pi}{(hc)^3}\int_{I_3}^\infty
       \frac{64\pi\alpha a_0^2}{3\sqrt3\,3^5}\Bigl(\frac{I_1}{E}\Bigr)^3E^2e^{-E/k_BT}dE.$$
   合并前置因子并写出$I_3=I_1/9$：
   $$\Gamma_{3c}
     =\frac{512\pi^2\alpha a_0^2I_1^3}{729\sqrt3\,h^3c^2}
       \int_{I_3}^\infty E^{-1}e^{-E/k_BT}dE
     \approx\frac{512\pi^2\alpha a_0^2I_1^3}{729\sqrt3\,h^3c^2}
       \frac{k_BT}{I_3}e^{-I_3/k_BT}$$
   $$\;=\frac{512\pi^2\alpha a_0^2I_1^2k_BT}{81\sqrt3\,h^3c^2}
     e^{-I_1/(9k_BT)}.$$

2. 辐射衰变速率  
   $$\Lambda_{3\to2}
     =\frac{4\alpha\omega_{32}^3}{3c^2\,g_3}S_{3\to2}
     =\frac{4\alpha}{3c^2\cdot18}(216a_0^2)\Bigl(\frac{5I_1}{36\hbar}\Bigr)^3$$
   $$\;=\frac{16\alpha a_0^2}{c^2}\Bigl(\frac{5I_1}{36\hbar}\Bigr)^3
     =\frac{125\alpha a_0^2I_1^3}{2916\,\hbar^3c^2}.$$

3. 比率  
   $$\mathcal{R}
     =\frac{\Gamma_{3c}}{\Lambda_{3\to2}}
     =\frac{\displaystyle\frac{512\pi^2\alpha a_0^2I_1^2k_BT}{81\sqrt3\,h^3c^2}
            e^{-I_1/(9k_BT)}}
           {\displaystyle\frac{125\alpha a_0^2I_1^3}{2916\,\hbar^3c^2}}
     =\frac{512\pi^2I_1^2k_BT}{81\sqrt3\,h^3}
       \frac{2916\,\hbar^3}{125I_1^3}
       e^{-I_1/(9k_BT)}$$
   使用 $\hbar^3/h^3=(1/(2\pi))^3 = 1/(8\pi^3)$ 并化简常数 ($2916/81=36$)：
   $$\mathcal{R}
     = \frac{512\pi^2 \cdot 36}{\sqrt{3} \cdot 125} \frac{1}{8\pi^3} \frac{k_B T}{I_1} e^{-I_1/(9k_BT)}
     =\frac{2304}{125\sqrt3\,\pi}
      \frac{k_BT}{I_1}\exp\!\Bigl(-\frac{I_1}{9k_BT}\Bigr).$$
